363
00:23:33,544 --> 00:23:34,472
Did I allow you to ask?

364
00:23:57,053 --> 00:23:57,992
(Letao Tower)

365
00:23:59,544 --> 00:24:00,144
It's for you.

366
00:24:00,745 --> 00:24:01,384
From who?

367
00:24:01,665 --> 00:24:02,696
Did I allow you to ask?

368
00:24:03,784 --> 00:24:04,544
