456
00:32:09,144 --> 00:32:09,705
Come with me.

457
00:32:16,624 --> 00:32:18,144
(Finally, you lose patience, huh?)

458
00:32:20,505 --> 00:32:20,985
Tiehan.

459
00:32:21,584 --> 00:32:22,505
Come on. Grab a meal.

460
00:32:22,665 --> 00:32:23,905
