464
00:32:30,025 --> 00:32:30,465
Okay.

465
00:32:31,505 --> 00:32:32,745
I'll head over first then.

466
00:32:33,104 --> 00:32:33,584
Take care.

467
00:32:33,584 --> 00:32:34,025
Okay.

